        	<li>IP address information is produced when you Agree/Disagree to Spots and when you post a new Spot. This information is stored on the server in relation to your account information. This information is not sold or given to third parties for commercial purposes. help.today may be forced by legal requirements to pass this information to government agencies.</li>
